YUSUF2.original: ~s~Hold ~INPUT_SPRINT~ while climbing a ladder to climb faster.
YUSUF2.translated: ~s~爬梯子时按住~INPUT_SPRINT~可以爬得更快。

YUSUF2.original: ~s~Take the ~y~elevator ~s~to the top of the tower.
~s~You have the parachute, now jump off the building.
YUSUF2.translated: ~s~你已获得降落伞，跳伞离开大楼。

YUSUF2.original: ~s~Use ~INPUT_SPRINT~ while climbing a ladder to climb faster.
YUSUF2.translated: ~s~爬梯子时按住~INPUT_SPRINT~可以爬得更快。

YUSUF2.original: When airborne use ~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~ to move. In freefall press ~INPUT_MOUSE_LMB~ to activate parachute. ~n~Hold ~INPUT_NEXT_CAMERA~ to view different cameras.
YUSUF2.translated: 用~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~在空中移动。~n~下落时按~INPUT_MOUSE_LMB~打开降落伞。~n~按住~INPUT_NEXT_CAMERA~查看不同视角。

YUSUF2.original: When airborne use ~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~ to move. In freefall press ~INPUT_SPRINT~ to activate parachute. ~n~Hold ~INPUT_MELEE_ATTACK1~ to view different cameras.
YUSUF2.translated: 用~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~在空中移动。~n~下落时按~INPUT_SPRINT~打开降落伞。~n~按住~INPUT_MELEE_ATTACK1~查看不同视角。

YUSUF2.original: ~s~Press ~INPUT_ENTER~ to mount the ladder. Use ~PAD_LSTICK_UPDOWN~ to move up and down on the ladder.
YUSUF2.translated: ~s~按~INPUT_ENTER~登上梯子，用~PAD_LSTICK_UPDOWN~在梯子上攀爬。

YUSUF2.original: Use ~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~ to shift body weight. ~n~Use ~INPUT_AIM~ and ~INPUT_ATTACK~ to apply left and right air brakes.~n~Press ~INPUT_ENTER~ to detach the parachute. ~n~Hold ~INPUT_MELEE_ATTACK1~ to view different cameras.
YUSUF2.translated: 用~PAD_LSTICK_ALL~控制身体重心。~n~按~INPUT_AIM~或~INPUT_ATTACK~进行急转。~n~按~INPUT_ENTER~脱离降落伞。~n~按住~INPUT_MELEE_ATTACK1~查看不同视角。

YUSUF2.original: While using a parachute, an altimeter will appear over the radar. This indicates your height above sea level.
YUSUF2.translated: 使用降落伞时，小地图上会显示高度计，指示当前的海拔高度。
